<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3145669" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="CHG" oldref="3"><variable id="flat_icons"><link href="text/shared/guide/flat_icons.xhp" name="Changing Icon Views">Changing Icon Size</link>
</variable></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3155535" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="4">You can change the icon view between small and large icons.</paragraph>
<list type="ordered">
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3153748" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="5">Choose <emph><switchinline select="sys"><caseinline select="MAC">%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</caseinline><defaultinline>Tools - Options</defaultinline></switchinline> - $[officename]</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3163802" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="6">On the <emph>View</emph> tab page, select the <emph>Toolbar icon size</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3157909" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="7">Click <emph>OK</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
</list>
